    "description": "This carb smart recipe replaces half the white rice for cauliflower rice. This dish'll teach you how to crisp tofu like a pro. Once golden brown, you'll serve it with sesame rice and a generous drizzle of sweet and spicy satay sauce. So satay-sfying!",
